<div class="jws-page">
  <section class="jws-page-hero">
    <div class="jws-page-hero__inner">
      <p class="jws-eyebrow">Independent maker business</p>
      <h1>About Josh's Widgets</h1>
      <p>Josh's Widgets is an independent maker business focused on practical parts that solve small but frustrating problems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="jws-page-body">
    <div class="jws-page-body__inner jws-split">
      <div>
        <h2>Accessories Should Look Like They Belong</h2>
        <p>The idea is simple: an accessory should look like it belongs where it is installed, not like an afterthought stuck onto something else.</p>
        <p>Josh designs helmet-specific Cardo adapter mounts and other useful accessories for riders, drivers, and enthusiasts. Every product begins with hands-on design work and moves through printing, finishing, inspection, packaging, and support before it reaches the customer.</p>
        <p>The goal is to make practical parts that fit well, look clean, and solve a real problem.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="jws-fit-graphic" role="img" aria-label="Abstract workshop process graphic">
        <div class="jws-fit-graphic__plate">
          <div class="jws-fit-graphic__line"><span>Design</span><span class="jws-fit-graphic__value">Hands-on</span></div>
          <div class="jws-fit-graphic__line"><span>Production</span><span class="jws-fit-graphic__value">Small batch</span></div>
          <div class="jws-fit-graphic__line"><span>Support</span><span class="jws-fit-graphic__value">Direct</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="jws-section jws-section--white">
    <div class="jws-section__inner">
      <div class="jws-section__header">
        <p class="jws-eyebrow">From idea to finished part</p>
        <h2>The Process</h2>
      </div>
      <ol class="jws-process">
        <li><span>Identify a real-world problem</span></li>
        <li><span>Design and test the part</span></li>
        <li><span>Print using appropriate materials</span></li>
        <li><span>Finish and inspect every piece</span></li>
        <li><span>Package and ship directly to customers</span></li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Josh's Widgets page",
  "enabled_on": {
    "templates": ["page"]
  },
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "About Josh's Widgets page"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
